ActCanadian Tourism Commission Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Industry of SHAUN HARBOTTLE of Whiteshell Post Office, Manitoba, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian Tourism Commission to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Deborah Greening.
